              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href={`https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=${encodeURIComponent(currentUrl)}`} 
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="text-gray-400 hover:text-[#3b5998] transition-colors"
               aria-label="Share on Facebook">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href={`https://wa.me/?text=${encodeURIComponent(title + ' ' + currentUrl)}`}
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="text-gray-400 hover:text-[#25D366] transition-colors social-share-whatsapp"
               aria-label="Share on WhatsApp">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M20.5027 3.49794C18.2187 1.2139 15.2335 0 12.0455 0C5.4635 0 0.091 5.37249 0.091 11.9545C0.091 14.0689 0.7005 16.1445 1.84423 17.9395L0 24L6.21574 22.1979C7.94772 23.2409 9.97293 23.8182 12.04 23.8182H12.0455C18.6275 23.8182 24 18.4457 24 11.8637C24 8.67575 22.7867 5.78199 20.5027 3.49794ZM12.0455 21.8109C10.2596 21.8109 8.50766 21.2558 6.99913 20.213L6.63308 19.9819L2.87409 21.0471L3.9503 17.3822L3.69732 17.0049C2.5536 15.4341 1.93919 13.5665 1.93919 11.9545C1.93919 6.48648 6.57752 1.84814 12.0455 1.84814C14.7092 1.84814 17.204 2.85252 19.0627 4.71117C20.9214 6.56982 21.9257 9.06467 21.9257 11.7284C22.1514 17.1964 17.5131 21.8109 12.0455 21.8109ZM17.4855 14.4686C17.204 14.3334 15.7783 13.638 15.5244 13.5484C15.2706 13.4589 15.0784 13.4364 14.8865 13.718C14.6943 13.9995 14.1392 14.6499 13.9747 14.842C13.8101 15.0342 13.6456 15.0566 13.364 14.9215C11.7655 14.1489 10.7158 13.547 9.66627 11.7284C9.36841 11.2184 10.0181 11.2635 10.6278 10.044C10.7158 9.85184 10.6711 9.68218 10.6052 9.54696C10.5392 9.41174 9.91192 7.98608 9.67705 7.42304C9.44743 6.88749 9.20451 6.96063 9.03128 6.94905C8.85643 6.94005 8.66977 6.94005 8.4779 6.94005C8.28604 6.94005 7.9781 7.00603 7.72429 7.28762C7.47049 7.56921 6.73066 8.26461 6.73066 9.69027C6.73066 11.1159 7.74613 12.5 7.9004 12.6918C8.05467 12.8837 9.89084 15.6107 12.6085 16.8851C14.3405 17.7034 15.0449 17.7711 15.9556 17.6134C16.5187 17.5126 17.6701 16.8851 17.9056 16.2095C18.1412 15.5339 18.1412 14.9708 18.0752 14.842C18.0157 14.6949 17.7671 14.6049 17.4855 14.4686Z"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-slate prose-lg">
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            PrimoTech LLC ("PrimoTech", and "we/us") places the highest priority on protecting users' personal 
            information and privacy. We have established this Privacy Policy to inform users about how their information is collected, used, 
            shared, stored, and protected. This Privacy Policy will help you understand how we process your personal information. This 
            Privacy Policy is directly related to the products and/or services of PrimoTech that you use.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-8">
            Please ensure that you thoroughly read and fully understand this Privacy Policy before using any products and/or services of PrimoTech, 
            and make appropriate choices based on your understanding. You should discontinue using any products and/or services of 
            PrimoTech immediately if you disagree with any content contained herein.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-8">
            This Privacy Policy applies exclusively to information we collect about you on or through our website, in electronic communications between you 
            and our website, and through mobile and desktop applications you download from our website. By accessing our website, you acknowledge that you have agreed to our processing of your personal 
            information in accordance with this Policy.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-8">
            If you have any questions, comments, or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal information, please contact us by sending an email to <strong>privacy@primotechllc.com</strong>.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">This Policy Will Help You Understand The Following:</h2>
          <ul class="mb-8">
            <li>I. Scope Of Information Collection</li>
            <li>II. Methods Of Information Collection</li>
            <li>III. Use Of Information</li>
            <li>IV. Sharing Of Information</li>
            <li>V. Storage And Protection Of Information</li>
            <li>VI. Your Rights</li>
            <li>VII. Third Party Services</li>
            <li>VIII. Transfer Of Personal Information Outside Of Your Jurisdiction</li>
            <li>IX. Privacy Of Minors</li>
            <li>X. Use Of Cookies</li>
            <li>XI. Contact Us</li>
            <li>XII. Revision Of Privacy Policy</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">I. Scope Of Information Collection</h2>
          <p>
            Personal information and non-personal information may be collected by us when you use PrimoTech products and/or services.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            <strong>Personal information</strong> refers to any information that relates to an identified natural person and that may be used to identify such natural person when combined with other information, including but not limited to name, gender, ID number, date of birth, residence, telephone number, email address, mailing address, and personal video content.
          </p>

          <p>
            <strong>Non-personal information</strong> refers to data other than personal information that cannot directly identify any specific person, such as profession, language, postal code, area code, serial number, URL, automatically recorded access data (browser type, domain name, web browsing frequency, referral webpage, IP address, and page navigation), unique product identifier, video content without personal information, device connection location and time zone, geographical location, mobile operator identification, device software platform, and hardware information.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">II. Methods Of Information Collection</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-light text-gray-800 mb-2">(I) PrimoTech Collects Your Personal Information Through The Following Methods:</h3>
          
          <p><strong>2.1 When you create an account and activate a PrimoTech product:</strong></p>
          <p>
            When you create an account to utilize PrimoTech services or register to access online videos, you agree to provide personal information. We collect your username, password, email address, and mobile phone number. Mobile phone numbers are collected to comply with network real-name system requirements of relevant laws and regulations. When you install and activate a product that requires connection to PrimoTech services and binding with your account, we may request basic product information such as product name, verification code, and serial number. Refusing to provide this information may prevent proper use of our products and/or services.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.2 When you log into applications through which PrimoTech provides services:</strong></p>
          <p>
            We collect device type, username, quantity, device login mode, application usage time, number of simultaneous live views, current mobile device model, operating system and version, and network connection information.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.3 When you save videos using PrimoTech services:</strong></p>
          <p>
            If you wish to save content such as video clips, live streaming, images, and message alerts, we collect video screenshots from your camera and push them to you. You can disable this function through your account settings.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.4 When you use message alert functions:</strong></p>
          <p>
            We may collect the unique characteristic value of your client device to provide accurate alarm message notifications. You can choose to disable this function and clear the unique characteristic value.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.5 When you use device addition functions:</strong></p>
          <p>
            We may collect device serial number, registration code, password, model, and client Wi-Fi information for network configuration and binding.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.6 When you use our device access service:</strong></p>
          <p>
            To ensure proper service operation, we collect device model, unique identifier, IP address, MAC address, software version, network access methods and types, location data (if device supports), and operation records.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.7 Additional collection scenarios include:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Real-time preview functions requiring device serial number, IP, port, and video stream information</li>
            <li>Analysis and comparison functions requiring reference information (face/human recognition, license plate/vehicle recognition, fingerprint data)</li>
            <li>Device sharing functions requiring device serial number, nickname, and shared user information</li>
            <li>Device operation control requiring device serial number, status, and operation behavior data</li>
            <li>Customer support requiring contact information, device details, and account verification</li>
            <li>Security monitoring in locations where PrimoTech audio/video devices are installed</li>
            <li>Employment applications through our official website requiring resume information</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-light text-gray-800 mb-2">(II) PrimoTech Collects Your Non-Personal Information Through The Following Methods:</h3>
          
          <p><strong>2.8 Service usage analysis:</strong></p>
          <p>
            We collect non-personal information according to industry standards to improve user experience, prevent misuse, and ensure normal service operation. This includes cookies, web beacons, pixel tags, and other technologies for recording settings, improving advertising effectiveness, and collecting log and device data.
          </p>

          <p><strong>2.9 User content processing:</strong></p>
          <p>
            When you use recording or streaming functions, we may record and transmit videos and/or audio with your consent, including screenshots and data analysis for identification purposes.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">III. Use Of Information</h2>
          <p>During your account existence or our service provision period, PrimoTech may use your collected personal information for the following purposes:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li>Responding to your inquiries and providing customer support</li>
            <li>Evaluating employment applications</li>
            <li>Enhancing website security through user identity verification, fraud detection, and data backup</li>
            <li>Conducting internal audits, data analysis, and research</li>
            <li>Sending electronic communications about latest products and services (with your consent)</li>
            <li>Improving user experience and service design through behavior analysis (with your consent)</li>
            <li>Complying with legal obligations and protecting our legitimate interests</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">IV. Sharing Of Information</h2>
          <p><strong>We Do Not Sell Any Personal Information To Third Parties And Never Will.</strong></p>
          
          <p>We limit access to your personal information on a need-to-know basis and require our employees to respect confidentiality and protect information according to this Policy.</p>

          <p><strong>We Will Share Your Personal Information In The Following Circumstances:</strong></p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>With PrimoTech affiliates</strong> when necessary to achieve purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy</li>
            <li><strong>With authorized partners</strong> to provide better customer service and user experience, including SMS operators for account registration, mobile manufacturers for alarm notifications, and cloud service providers for core video monitoring functions</li>
            <li><strong>User-initiated sharing</strong> when you choose to share videos, identity information, or location data with specific or unspecified recipients</li>
            <li><strong>Legal compliance</strong> to comply with applicable laws and regulations and provide better customer service</li>
            <li><strong>Legal requirements</strong> without your consent when required by law, including national security matters, public safety issues, criminal investigations, life-threatening emergencies, publicly disclosed information, contract requirements, service stability maintenance, academic research, and legal proceedings</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">V. Storage And Protection Of Information</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-light text-gray-800 mb-2">(I) Duration And Location Of Information Storage</h3>
          <p>
            Your personal information is stored by PrimoTech only for purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Information collected during operations is stored in applicable business locations. Your personal information will be stored continuously while you use our products or receive our services, unless longer storage duration is required by law or you provide express authorization.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-light text-gray-800 mb-2">(II) Protection Of Information</h3>
          <p>
            We prioritize information security with a dedicated team researching and applying administrative, technical, and physical security controls. We implement data encryption, access control mechanisms, internal control systems, and regular security assessments. We maintain ISO27001 certification and engage external third parties for security evaluations. However, absolute security cannot be guaranteed due to technological limitations and evolving cyber threats.
          </p>

          <p>
            Information security also depends on your cooperation. You are responsible for keeping login credentials confidential. We provide emergency response plans for security incidents and will notify you through push notifications or announcements if personal information breaches occur.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">VI. Your Rights</h2>
          
          <p>You can access and update personal information through your account or contact us at <strong>support@primotechllc.com</strong>. Subject to applicable laws, you have the following rights:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li>Access or correct your personal information</li>
            <li>Delete your personal information</li>
            <li>Change authorization scope or revoke consent</li>
            <li>Deregister your account</li>
            <li>Obtain copies of your personal information</li>
            <li>Opt out of direct marketing and refuse cookie usage</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            EU residents have additional rights including consent, access, rectification, data portability, and data erasure rights. You may file complaints with data protection authorities if concerned about our information processing practices.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">VII. Third Party Services</h2>
          
          <p>Our products and services may access or link to third-party websites or services, including:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li>Social sharing buttons that may collect information and log data</li>
            <li>Third-party SDKs for message push functions, device location services, account security, and data encryption</li>
            <li>Partner services for enhanced functionality and user experience</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            We share information only for legitimate, necessary, and specific purposes. Third-party service providers must perform confidentiality obligations and implement appropriate security measures. Our Privacy Policy does not cover third-party cookie usage or data practices.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">VIII. Transfer Of Personal Information Outside Of Your Jurisdiction</h2>
          
          <p>
            When transferring personal information outside your jurisdiction to affiliated companies or third-party service providers, we comply with applicable laws and regulations. For EU transfers, we implement EU standard contractual clauses or other GDPR safeguards. As a globally operating company, we may transfer personal data to PrimoTech subsidiaries worldwide and third-party service providers outside the European Economic Area while maintaining appropriate safeguards.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">IX. Privacy Of Minors</h2>
          
          <p>
            We do not provide services to minors under 18 years of age (or applicable minimum age in relevant jurisdiction). We immediately delete accounts connected to or registered by minors and attempt to delete personal information collected from minors without verifiable parental consent. Parents or guardians may contact us to examine, delete, or restrict use of their minor's personal information.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">X. Use Of Cookies</h2>
          
          <p>
            We use cookies and similar technologies to record preferences, improve advertising effectiveness, and collect non-identifying information. This helps us understand service usage, diagnose problems, and improve our services. You can configure your browser to detect and reject cookies. Please refer to our separate Cookie Policy for detailed information.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">XI. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions, comments, or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal information, please contact us at <strong>privacy@primotechllc.com</strong>. We will respond within 15 working days after reviewing and verifying your identity.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-4">XII. Revision Of Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy was last revised on January 1, 2024. We may revise this Privacy Policy periodically, and such revisions become integral parts of this Policy. When policy terms change, we will notify you through push notifications and pop-up windows upon login. We will collect, use, and store your personal information according to the updated policy only after you click the Agree button in the notification window.
          </p>
          
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
            <p>Effective Date: January 1, 2024</p>
            <p>Last Updated: January 1, 2024</p>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Whatsapp client:load />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .prose h3 {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #374151;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .contact-info {
    padding: 1rem;
    background-color: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
  }
  
  /* Social sharing icons */
  .social-share-icon {
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .social-share-icon:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .social-share-whatsapp {
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .social-share-whatsapp::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    background: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  
